OL,5,G0420 Simon Reeve's South America
OL,6,     FSimon Reeve journeys through the
OL,7,     Fremote northeast of South America
OL,8,     Ffrom the spectacular Mount Roraima
OL,9,     Fin Venezuela through Guyana,
OL,10,     FSuriname, and French Guiana.
OL,11,G0510 Simon Reeve's South America
OL,12,     FSimon travels through Brazil,
OL,13,     Fvisiting a neglected indigenous
OL,14,     Fneighbourhood in Manaus and
OL,15,     Fmeeting a nurse who was the only
OL,16,     Fsource of healthcare during the
OL,17,     Fpandemic.
